","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[472,3714,5273,12230,20242],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"海关总署新闻发言人、统计分析司司长吕大良介绍，9月当月，我国出口2.17万亿元，增长了1.6%，增速确实有所放缓，初步分析，主要是受一些短期偶发因素的影响。首先，跟9月份的极端天气有一定的关系，9月两次台风接连在长三角地区登陆，历史数据也显示，台风对出口的影响持续时间比较长，台风过后船队的排期往往会顺延，出口有所滞后。其次，前段时间受全球航运不畅、集装箱短缺，以及美国东海岸码头工人合同到期谈判预期等的影响，企业的出货、物流节奏有所调整，数据也显示，部分产品往年出口旺季是在三季度，今年提前了一个多月。此外，去年9月出口规模基数是比较高的，是年内的次高，仅次于12月份，基数偏高也制约了今年9月的同比增速。总的来说，9月当月出口增速的放缓属于短期内正常的数据波动。 海关总署：9月我国出口2.17万亿元，增长1.6% _ 东方财富网"},"attached_info":"Cj8IqNfPwrrKrpc5EAMaCTExMTE0NTkyOCDFwLO4BjAAOGlADHIJODg3NzQxNzQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-3a6f5c141fd271e8e9ba2a6beadb79dc_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1729005546.387132","card_id":"Q_717764564","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":717764564,"title":"如果你突然遇见了那个在你心里挂念了许久的人，但已经十年不曾联系，你还会跟他打招呼吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/717764564","type":"question","created":1727850507,"answer_count":185,"follower_count":204,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[11605,11762,18028,28476],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIqNfPwrrKrpc5EAMaCTExMDg5ODkwMiCL0PO3BjAAOMwBQA1yCTcxNzc2NDU2NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5ebede75c78017a779b4324b68d9c45e_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"14_1729005546.387458","card_id":"Q_26570985","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce